<link href="adcp.css" rel="stylesheet"><entry><xh5>have word • have words</xh5><p> <i>have word—</i>receive a message: After about four months, in May, we <u>had word</u> that this comet was going to impact Jupiter. </p><p><i>have words—</i>have a quarrel: Every time the two of them get together they <u>have words</u>.</p><p> <div class="note">Note</div> The expression is not antonymous in meaning to the phrase <b>have no words</b>—be unable to describe or talk about smth.: We all here are quite astonished and <u>have no words</u> to describe the situation.</p> </entry>
